river-adventure-house.jpg.description: The whale is a blue decorative figure positioned at the top of the yellow water slide, situated in the upper left area of the image.

construction-evening.jpg.description: A person riding a horse is located on the left side of the image, near the hill. The horse is brown, and the rider is dressed in a black outfit, possibly wearing a helmet. Nearby, there is construction equipment and people engaged in various activities on the site.

The castle is located in the upper right corner of the image. It is situated on top of a hill amidst autumn-colored trees. The castle features multiple turrets and red-roofed spires, and is illuminated by the moonlight.

kf-winter.jpg.description: The sun is located in the upper right corner of the image. It is a small, orange circle against the light grayish sky, adding a warm contrast to the snowy scene.

The log cabin is located in the lower left section of the image. It's a rectangular structure with a green roof and light brown walls. There are people standing outside, engaged in various activities.

construction-site.jpg.description: The fox is located on the roof of a white building, towards the left side of the image. It is orange with a bushy tail and is sitting, looking forward.

The concrete mixer truck is located on the left side of the image. It is green with a striped mixing drum and is parked with its front facing to the left. Two people wearing construction hats are nearby.

construction-snow.jpg.description: The Santa is located near the top right, standing next to a yellow building. Santa is depicted in traditional red attire with a white beard.

The sedan is a red car located towards the lower right of the image. It is partially covered in snow, being cleared by a man with a large snowball. Nearby, there are children making snowmen and a person in green attire near a Christmas tree.

mitgutsch-beach.jpg.description: The pirate flag is located near the top center of the image. It is black with a white skull and crossbones design. The flag is attached to a small pole on a sandy area near a wooden platform where children are playing. Several characters are nearby, including a child playing with a toy near the flag.

mitgutsch-carnival.jpg.description: A chef wearing a white chef's hat is located in the central area of the image. The chef is holding a balancing scale with two orange balls in each hand. A group of people are actively engaging around the chef.

mitgutsch-fight.jpg.description: The man waving a white flag is located in the bottom right portion of the image. He is wearing a white outfit, lying on the ground on his back, and holding a white flag up in the air. Nearby, there are people in animated poses, and the floor is wooden.

mitgutsch-orchestra.jpg.description: A person sitting on a flight case in the bottom left corner is holding a mandarin orange in their left hand. The orange is small and round, typical in color for a mandarin.

mitgutsch-pirate.jpg.description: The couple is located near the top right corner, just below the sign that reads 'Käthes Küche.' They are standing on a wooden platform, embracing each other with a kiss. The man is wearing a blue shirt, and the woman has long hair. There are other people on the platform around them.

mitgutsch-pool.jpg.description: The tennis racket is located on the left side of the image, near the top. It is leaning against a small structure among trees and people, and appears to be orange or brown in color.

mitgutsch-townsquare.jpg.description: The kite is located towards the top-center of the image, above a tree. It is a diamond-shaped kite with a red and white checkered pattern, being flown by a person who is sitting on a bench.

mitgutsch-water.jpg.description: The lobster is located in the bottom left section of the image. It is in the hands of a person wearing a white outfit near the edge of the water. The lobster is red and is prominently visible against the person's white clothing.

tigertom-park3.jpg.description: The cartoon tiger is standing upright near the middle of the image. It is yellow with black stripes and has a friendly expression. It is wearing a green and yellow outfit and is visible just behind the pathway where people are walking, close to some bushes and trees.
The soccer ball is located in the bottom right portion of the image. It is a classic black and white patterned ball, actively being kicked by a child wearing a red shirt and black shorts.
